You set a lineup each playoff week with all players available to each team. You can only use a player once and then he’s locked out for future weeks. As NFL teams lose and you use up players, the player pool shrinks for your lineup. Total fantasy points wins the league. 1st $400, 2nd $200, 3rd $50

It’s a PPR league with the tight end position getting 1.5 PPR and all others 1 PPR. Other than that th scoring is pretty standard.


League requirements:
 	Req	Current	Avail
Total	9	0	9
QB	1	0	1
RB	2-3	0	3
WR	2-3	0	3
TE	1-2	0	2
PK	0-1	0	1
Def	0-1	0	1
